---Lokk/Axis---

Lokk and Axis receive Zeni's signature, and begins searching. Not 
long after they pick up his signal with several other bots, and 
Windlord. They head over, weaving in and out of trees, enjoying the 
crisp cool air. Lokk opens a commlink to Seekker, "Seekker, get 
over here, I think that our target has been found." commlink closed. 
He and Axis come up beside Windlord. Lokk blinks, "New bots... 
Windlord, who're these bots?" Axis check's over his shoulder for 
Seekker.
